<html><head><title>Hunt</title></head> <body bgcolor="#000000" text="#FFFFFF" vlink = "#99cccc" link = "#99ccff"  topmargin=0leftmargin=0 ><TABLE border = "0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="5"><TR><TD valign = middle align = left  height = 300 ><font size="+1">I carried 113 dead Marines at Tam KY one day in May of '67. Mostsickening site that I had, up until then, seen. My gunner threw up. The smell... whatit  meant...then prisoners were put on our planes to be taken out of thearea and questioned. Imagine the little smart asses grinning. defiant? No.Just scared and trying to be not-scared.  A knife under their throats andthe grins became <A HREF = "hunt4.html">tremblings</A>.</font> <p>JJoel Hunt Sr.</TD></TR></table></body></html>